  "detailed_description": "<h1>See also</h1><p><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1648748963\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Challenge yourself in this minimalistic puzzle game about musical melodies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1648748963\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Connect the blocks</h2>Move freely around the scenery and connect the blocks in the form you think will solve the puzzle<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/f5032317598fb3e5d6c152e090981788.poster.avif?t=1648748963\" width=410 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/f5032317598fb3e5d6c152e090981788.webm?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/f5032317598fb3e5d6c152e090981788.mp4?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve the puzzle</h2>Try and connect the blocks in the way described on the level, once you reach the position you completed it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/72170a5f37552e2871ec6a0ab8baeedb.poster.avif?t=1648748963\" width=662 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/72170a5f37552e2871ec6a0ab8baeedb.webm?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/72170a5f37552e2871ec6a0ab8baeedb.mp4?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the Melody</h2>Once you solve the puzzle a piece of melody will be unlocked, do you know them? (Based on over 30 popular melodies)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/e9e9562190b8e59a2f06370af9c8721a.poster.avif?t=1648748963\" width=410 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/e9e9562190b8e59a2f06370af9c8721a.webm?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/e9e9562190b8e59a2f06370af9c8721a.mp4?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy the process!</h2>Move, connect, solve and discover in over 50 hand-crafted levels in an easy and intuitive way<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/2ae7fdcb5cf2efe1d588a2ee69f22dab.poster.avif?t=1648748963\" width=800 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/2ae7fdcb5cf2efe1d588a2ee69f22dab.webm?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/2ae7fdcb5cf2efe1d588a2ee69f22dab.mp4?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Remember, you can always undo your actions till the beginning of each level<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/7093909f9bbe929eadea0abacaa16828.poster.avif?t=1648748963\" width=378 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/7093909f9bbe929eadea0abacaa16828.webm?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/7093909f9bbe929eadea0abacaa16828.mp4?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you like the game, <u>Wishlist now!</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1648748963\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1648748963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
